{"type":"step_start","timestamp":1775862091109,"sessionID":"ses_2865f3a92ffeXRnTsVGMIrH1Lv","part":{"id":"prt_d79a10d62001X6c3D3jLrLPVcy","messageID":"msg_d79a10118001N4OglqYGsN1YqU","sessionID":"ses_2865f3a92ffeXRnTsVGMIrH1Lv","snapshot":"f33c5114db06c230ebdbad281b75532a26b6f114","type":"step-start"}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775862147862,"sessionID":"ses_2865f3a92ffeXRnTsVGMIrH1Lv","part":{"id":"prt_d79a1128c001B0VwGOPgXsae0H","messageID":"msg_d79a10118001N4OglqYGsN1YqU","sessionID":"ses_2865f3a92ffeXRnTsVGMIrH1Lv","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_da301472705a4ab5ab880efb","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# Delta Spec: AR-022 — CLI publish 命令\n\n## Overview\n\nThis delta-spec defines acceptance scenarios for implementing the CLI publish command in the AgentCube CLI tool (`kubectl-agentcube`).\n\n## Base Specifications\n\n- **AR**: AR-022\n- **Module**: `cmd/cli`\n- **Language**: Python\n- **Size**: L\n\n---\n\n## Background\n\n(TODO: Describe the publish command purpose and workflow)\n\n---\n\n## Requirements\n\n### AR-022-001: CLI interface\n\nThe system SHALL expose the `publish` command via Typer with specific options.\n\n#### Scenario: AR-022-001-A — Publish command options\n\n- **GIVEN** the user runs `kubectl-agentcube publish --help`\n- **THEN** the CLI SHALL display:\n  - (TODO: Define CLI options)\n\n#### Scenario: AR-022-001-B — Default options\n\n- **GIVEN** the user runs `publish` with no options\n- **THEN** defaults SHALL be applied:\n  - (TODO: Define defaults)\n\n---\n\n### AR-022-002: Publish prerequisites validation\n\nThe system SHALL validate publish prerequisites before proceeding.\n\n#### Scenario: AR-022-002-A — Validate workspace exists\n\n- **GIVEN** the specified workspace path does not exist\n- **WHEN** validation runs\n- **THEN** the system SHALL raise `FileNotFoundError`\n\n#### Scenario: AR-022-002-B — Validate metadata exists\n\n- **GIVEN** the workspace does not contain `agent_metadata.yaml`\n- **WHEN** publish runs\n- **THEN** the system SHALL raise `FileNotFoundError`\n\n#### Scenario: AR-022-002-C — Validate image exists\n\n- **GIVEN** required container image does not exist\n- **WHEN** publish runs\n- **THEN** the system SHALL raise `RuntimeError`\n\n---\n\n### AR-022-003: Registry publish\n\nThe system SHALL publish the container image to a container registry.\n\n#### Scenario: AR-022-003-A — Publish to registry\n\n- **GIVEN** valid image and registry configuration\n- **WHEN** publish runs\n- **THEN** the system SHALL push the image to the registry\n\n#### Scenario: AR-022-003-B — Publish with custom registry\n\n- **GIVEN** `--registry` option is provided\n- **WHEN** publish runs\n- **THEN** the system SHALL push to the specified registry\n\n#### Scenario: AR-022-003-C — Publish with authentication\n\n- **GIVEN** registry credentials are configured\n- **WHEN** publish runs\n- **THEN** the system SHALL authenticate before pushing\n\n#### Scenario: AR-022-003-D — Publish failure handling\n\n- **GIVEN** registry push fails\n- **WHEN** publish runs\n- **THEN** the system SHALL propagate the error\n- **AND** exit with code `1`\n\n---\n\n### AR-022-004: Registry authentication\n\nThe system SHALL handle registry authentication securely.\n\n#### Scenario: AR-022-004-A — Use configured credentials\n\n- **GIVEN** credentials are configured in config file\n- **WHEN** publish runs\n- **THEN** the system SHALL use those credentials\n\n#### Scenario: AR-022-004-B — Login on demand\n\n- **GIVEN** `--login` option is provided\n- **WHEN** publish runs\n- **THEN** the system SHALL perform registry login first\n\n---\n\n### AR-022-005: Version handling\n\nThe system SHALL handle version information during publish.\n\n#### Scenario: AR-022-005-A — Use version from metadata\n\n- **GIVEN** metadata contains version\n- **WHEN** publish runs\n- **THEN** the system SHALL tag image with that version\n\n#### Scenario: AR-022-005-B — Custom tag\n\n- **GIVEN** `--tag` option is provided\n- **WHEN** publish runs\n- **THEN** the system SHALL use the custom tag\n\n---\n\n### AR-022-006: Publish metadata update\n\nThe system SHALL update workspace metadata with publish results.\n\n#### Scenario: AR-022-006-A — Update metadata after publish\n\n- **GIVEN** publish completes successfully\n- **WHEN** metadata is updated\n- **THEN** the system SHALL save registry URL and publish timestamp\n\n---\n\n### AR-022-007: Error handling\n\nThe system SHALL handle errors with appropriate error messages and exit codes.\n\n#### Scenario: AR-022-007-A — Publish error with verbose logging\n\n- **GIVEN** publish raises an exception\n- **WHEN** `--verbose` flag is enabled\n- **THEN** the CLI SHALL print error message with full traceback\n- **AND** exit with code `1`\n\n#### Scenario: AR-022-007-B — Publish error without verbose\n\n- **GIVEN** publish raises an exception\n- **WHEN** `--verbose` flag is NOT enabled\n- **THEN** the CLI SHALL print error message without traceback\n- **AND** exit with code `1`\n\n---\n\n### AR-022-008: Successful publish output\n\nThe system SHALL display success messages with publish details.\n\n#### Scenario: AR-022-008-A — Display publish success\n\n- **GIVEN** publish completes successfully\n- **WHEN** the command finishes\n- **THEN** the CLI SHALL display success message with:\n  - Registry URL\n  - Image full name\n  - Publish timestamp\n\n---\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n- [ ] AC001: Publish command accepts all specified CLI options\n- [ ] AC002: Publish validates workspace and metadata exist before proceeding\n- [ ] AC003: Publish validates image exists before pushing\n- [ ] AC004: Publish pushes image to specified registry\n- [ ] AC005: Publish handles registry authentication\n- [ ] AC006: Publish uses version from metadata or custom tag\n- [ ] AC007: Publish metadata is updated with registry information\n- [ ] AC008: Publish displays success output with Rich formatting\n- [ ] AC009: Publish handles errors with appropriate exit codes and verbose logging\n\n---\n\n## Architecture Notes\n\n### Key Components\n\n| Component | Path | Description |\n|-----------|------|-------------|\n| CLI Entry | `agentcube/cli/main.py` | Typer app with `publish` command |\n| PublishRuntime | `agentcube/runtime/publish_runtime.py` | Core publish logic |\n| RegistryService | `agentcube/services/registry_service.py` | Registry operations |\n| DockerService | `agentcube/services/docker_service.py` | Docker SDK operations |\n| MetadataService | `agentcube/services/metadata_service.py` | Metadata CRUD operations |\n\n### Publish Flow\n\n```\npublish command\n    └─> PublishRuntime.publish()\n            ├─> _validate_publish_prerequisites()\n            ├─> _authenticate_registry()\n            ├─> _push_to_registry()\n            └─> _update_publish_metadata()\n```\n\n### CLI Options Mapping\n\n| CLI Option | Runtime Parameter | Type |\n|------------|-------------------|------|\n| `-f, --workspace` | workspace_path | str |\n| `-r, --registry` | options[\"registry\"] | Optional[str] |\n| `-t, --tag` | options[\"tag\"] | Optional[str] |\n| `--login` | options[\"login\"] | bool |\n| `--verbose` | verbose | bool |\n\n---\n\n## References\n\n- Base design: `cli-toolkit/design.md`\n- Base spec: `cli-toolkit/spec.md`\n- CLI entry point: `agentcube/cli/main.py`\n- Runtime implementation: `agentcube/runtime/publish_runtime.py`\n- Registry service: `agentcube/services/registry_service.py`\n- Docker service: `agentcube/services/docker_service.py`\n- Metadata model: `agentcube/services/metadata_service.py`\n- Related: AR-021 (build command)","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-022/delta-spec.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-022/delta-spec.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-022/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775862147844,"end":1775862147860}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775862147865,"sessionID":"ses_2865f3a92ffeXRnTsVGMIrH1Lv","part":{"id":"prt_d79a1986e001pC6w2g0L4Kydbz","messageID":"msg_d79a10118001N4OglqYGsN1YqU","sessionID":"ses_2865f3a92ffeXRnTsVGMIrH1Lv","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_53a0f64fa2854cf7ac4fe110","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-022 — CLI publish 命令 Tasks\n\n**Module:** cmd/cli  \n**Language:** Python  \n**Size:** L  \n**Stage:** ST-2 (Draft)\n\n---\n\n## Phase 1: RegistryService Implementation\n\n- [ ] **T101** Create `agentcube/services/registry_service.py` with `RegistryService` class\n  - *Verify:* `python -c \"from agentcube.services.registry_service import RegistryService; print('ok')\"`\n\n- [ ] **T102** Add `authenticate(registry_url, username, password)` method to `RegistryService`\n  - *Verify:* Method exists with correct signature\n\n- [ ] **T103** Add `push_image(image_name, registry_url, tag)` method to `RegistryService`\n  - *Verify:* Method exists with correct signature\n\n- [ ] **T104** Add `check_image_exists(image_name, registry_url)` method to `RegistryService`\n  - *Verify:* Method exists with correct signature\n\n---\n\n## Phase 2: PublishRuntime Implementation\n\n- [ ] **T201** Create `agentcube/runtime/publish_runtime.py` with `PublishRuntime` class\n  - *Verify:* `python -c \"from agentcube.runtime.publish_runtime import PublishRuntime; print('ok')\"`\n\n- [ ] **T202** Implement `_validate_publish_prerequisites(workspace_path)` method\n  - *Verify:* Raises `FileNotFoundError` for missing workspace/metadata/image\n\n- [ ] **T203** Implement `_authenticate_registry(registry_url, options)` method\n  - *Verify:* Handles authentication flow\n\n- [ ] **T204** Implement `_push_to_registry(workspace_path, metadata, options)` method\n  - *Verify:* Calls RegistryService.push_image with correct args\n\n- [ ] **T205** Implement `_update_publish_metadata(workspace_path, metadata, publish_result)` method\n  - *Verify:* Updates metadata with registry info and saves\n\n- [ ] **T206** Implement main `publish(workspace_path, **options)` method\n  - *Verify:* Full publish flow works\n\n---\n\n## Phase 3: CLI Integration\n\n- [ ] **T301** Add `publish` command to `agentcube/cli/main.py` Typer app\n  - *Verify:* `kubectl-agentcube publish --help`\n\n- [ ] **T302** Implement `publish` command options: `-f/--workspace`, `-r/--registry`, `-t/--tag`, `--login`, `--verbose`\n  - *Verify:* All options appear in `--help`\n\n- [ ] **T303** Connect `publish` command to `PublishRuntime.publish()` with error handling\n  - *Verify:* Error messages display correctly with `_handle_error`\n\n- [ ] **T304** Add success output with Rich formatting showing registry URL, image name, timestamp\n  - *Verify:* Rich Panel displays with correct fields\n\n---\n\n## Phase 4: Testing\n\n- [ ] **T401** Write unit tests for `PublishRuntime._validate_publish_prerequisites`\n  - *Verify:* `pytest tests/ -v -k \"test_validate_publish\"`\n\n- [ ] **T402** Write unit tests for `PublishRuntime._authenticate_registry`\n  - *Verify:* Authentication flow works correctly\n\n- [ ] **T403** Write unit tests for `PublishRuntime._push_to_registry`\n  - *Verify:* Mock RegistryService, verify correct calls\n\n- [ ] **T404** Write integration test for `publish` command end-to-end\n  - *Verify:* Full workflow with test workspace\n\n---\n\n## Phase 5: Verification Commands\n\n```bash\n# CLI help\nkubectl-agentcube publish --help\n\n# Basic publish (requires built workspace with metadata)\nkubectl-agentcube publish -f /path/to/workspace\n\n# Publish to custom registry\nkubectl-agentcube publish -f . -r registry.example.com\n\n# Publish with custom tag\nkubectl-agentcube publish -f . -t v1.0.0\n\n# Publish with login\nkubectl-agentcube publish -f . --login\n\n# Run all tests\npytest cmd/cli/tests/ -v\n\n# Run lint\nruff check agentcube/\nruff format agentcube/\n\n# Run typecheck\nmypy agentcube/\n```\n\n---\n\n## Dependencies\n\n- Requires: AR-021 (build command) completed\n- Uses: `agentcube/services/registry_service.py`\n- Uses: `agentcube/services/docker_service.py`\n- Uses: `agentcube/services/metadata_service.py`\n- Uses: `agentcube/runtime/build_runtime.py` (pattern reference)\n\n---\n\n## Notes\n\n- Design stage ST-2 draft - details to be finalized\n- Publish pushes built image to container registry\n- Supports custom registry and tag\n- Requires authentication for private registries","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-022/tasks.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-022/tasks.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-022/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775862147851,"end":1775862147863}}}}
